                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120408-72-defend798 t18120408-72-punish390"></join>
               Confined Six Months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18120408-72-punish391" type="punishmentDescription">
